OL,3,CHollywood star Rupert Everett pulling
OL,4,Cpints in battle to save local pub
OL,6,FActor Rupert Everett has been doing
OL,7,Fshifts behind the bar of his village
OL,8,Fpub to help save it from closure.
OL,10,FThe 66-year-old Hollywood star, known
OL,11,Ffor his roles in Another Country and
OL,12,FMy Best Friend's Wedding, has been
OL,13,Fhelping out The Swan in Enford, which
OL,14,Fis at risk of closure.
OL,16,FThe pub shut earlier this year when
OL,17,Fthe previous licensee left, and is now
OL,18,Fstaffed by a rotation of volunteers in
OL,19,Fa bid to keep the doors open.
