OL,3,CHollywood star Rupert Everett pulling
OL,4,Cpints in battle to save local pub
OL,6,FEverett told ITV's Good Morning
OL,7,FBritain: "I'm part of a big rota. Our
OL,8,Fpub closed down a few months ago, and
OL,9,Fit's had a chequered existence for the
OL,10,Flast 20 years, like many pubs.
OL,12,F"It's in a rural village, and I think
OL,13,Fthe people in the village realised
OL,14,Fthat without it, there's no
OL,15,Fpossibility of communication, and so
OL,16,Fthe villagers wanted to keep the pub
OL,17,Fgoing.
OL,19,F"Everybody decided to take part in
OL,20,Frotas in various roles, and I have
OL,21,Fdone a few stints pulling pints.
