OL,3,CHollywood star Rupert Everett pulling
OL,4,Cpints in battle to save local pub
OL,6,FHe added: "It's a great thing. Without
OL,7,Fa pub in a village, if you're in the
OL,8,Fcountryside and you're eight miles
OL,9,Ffrom the nearest town, it's sad, and
OL,10,Fit's such a difficult time for pubs in
OL,11,Fgeneral."
OL,13,FAsked if he has good arm action for
OL,14,Fpulling pints, Everett said: "I'm
OL,15,Fdoing pretty well so far."
OL,17,FHe added he would be back behind the
OL,18,Fbar "probably at the end of the month".
